author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Selective Insurance Group Says Tax Net Insured Catastrophe Losses Totaling About $26 Mln

organizations.name: brief-selective insurance group says tax net insured catastrophe losses

text:
April 9 (Reuters) - Selective Insurance Group Inc:
* SELECTIVE INSURANCE GROUP, INC. ANNOUNCES FIRST QUARTER CATASTROPHE LOSSES, OTHER PROPERTY LOSSES AND NET FAVORABLE RESERVE DEVELOPMENT
* TAX NET INSURED CATASTROPHE LOSSES TOTALING APPROXIMATELY $26 MILLION
* CATASTROPHE PROPERTY LOSSES WERE ABOVE EXPECTED BY $33 MILLION TO REDUCE EARNINGS PER SHARE BY $0.44 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
